<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/main.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Tangerine">
  <script src="/newWill.js"></script>
  
  <title>Free Willing</title>
</head>

<body>
  <form action="/newWill" method="post">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="formContainer">
        <label>Legal Name:  <input name="name" placeholder="name on passport or birth certificate"></label>
        <br>
        <label>City of Residence:  <input name="city" placeholder="e.g. Auckland"> 
            
            <div class="itemContainer">

            Executor(s) or Trustee(s)
            
            <label for="executor1">
            Executor 1:
            
            <input name="executor1" placeholder="Executor 1's Full Name"> 
            <input name="executor1city" placeholder="Executor 1's city of residence">
            <input name="executor1occ" placeholder="Excutor 1's occupation">
            </label>

            <br>
            <label for="executor2">
            Executor 2:
            <input name="Executor2" placeholder="Executor 2's Full Name"> 
            <input name="executor2city" placeholder="Executor 2's city of residence">
            <input name="executor2occ" laceholder="Excutor 2's occupation">
            </label>
            </div>

            <div class="beneficiary">
            Beneficiary/Beneficiaries:
            <br>
            <label for="ben1">
            <input type="radio" id="ben1" name="beneficiary" value="my spouse/partner">
            My spouse/partner <input type="text" name="beneficiaryName" class="hide" id="field1" placeholder="Legal Name">solely.</label>
            
            {{!-- Need event handler or js listen onclick of radio button with text input (hide the input text if it's not selected)...maybe do this with React later! --}}
            <br>
            <label for="ben2">
            <input type="radio" id="ben2" name="beneficiary" value="all my children equally, who survive me and attained the age of twenty (20) years. If any child dies before me but leaving a surviving child or children then such child or children shall taken the share of my estate (original and accruing) which his, her or their parent would have otherwise taken.">
            All my children equally. But if they die before me, my grandchildren who survive them.
            </label>
           
            <br>
            <label for="ben3">
            <input type="radio" id="ben3" name="beneficiary" value="my sibling">
            My sibling <input type="text" name="beneficiaryName" class="hide" id="field2" placeholder="Legal Name">solely. 
            </label>
            {{!-- ask how to put solely at the end of the name --}}
            
            <br>
            <label for="ben4">
            <input type="radio" id="ben4" name="beneficiary" value="siblings">
            My siblings <input type="text" name="beneficiaryName" class="hide" id="field3" placeholder="Legal Names">equally or if any of them predeceases me, to the survivors equally or the survivor solely.
            </label>

            <br>
            <label for="ben5">
            <input type="radio" id="ben5" name="beneficiary" value="parents">
            My parents <input type="text" name="beneficiaryName" class="hide" id="field4" placeholder="Legal Names">equally or if any of them predeceases me, to the survivor solely.
            </label>
            
            <br>
            </div>

            <div class="itemContainer">
            Residual Beneficiary/Beneficiaries:
            If the above beneficary dies before me, I wish to gift my estate to:
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="resBen"value="all my children equally, who survive me and attained the age of twenty (20) years. If any child dies before me but leaving a surviving child or children then such child or children shall taken the share of my estate (original and accruing) which his, her or their parent would have otherwise taken.">All my children equally. But if they die before me, my grandchildren who survive them.
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="resBen" value="my spouse/partner">my spouse/partner <input type="text" placeholder="Legal Name">solely.
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="resBen" value="my sibling">my sibling <input type="text" placeholder="Legal Name">solely.
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="resBen" value="my siblings">my siblings <input type="text" placeholder="Legal Names">equally or if any of them predeceases me, to the survivors equally or the survivor solely.  
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="resBen" value="my parents">my parents <input type="text" placeholder="Legal Names">equally or if any of them predeceases me, to the survivor solely.
            </div>
            

            <div class="itemContainer">
            I wish my bodily remains to be
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="remains" value="buried">buried at <input type="text" placeholder="specify place">
            <br>
            <input type="radio" name="remains" value="cremated">cremated and my ashes to be <input type="text" placeholder="e.g. scattered at Piha beach">
            </div>

            <div>
                Witnesses:
                <br>
                Witness 1: <input name="witness1" placeholder="Witness 1 Legal Name"> of <input name="witness1city" placeholder="city of residence">, <input name="witness1occ" placeholder="occupation">
                <br>
                Witness 2: <input name="witness2" placeholder="Witness 2 Legal Name"> of <input name="witness2city" placeholder="city of residence">, <input name="witness2occ" placeholder="occupation">
            </div>
            </div>

            <div class=createButton>   
            <button onclick="location.href='/html';">Create My Free Will</button>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </form>
    <pre id="log">
    </pre>

</body>

</html>